    "title": "Mission M090: Reconnaissance and Analysis of Unidentified Anomaly",
    "objective": "To identify the nature, origin, and potential threat level of an anomaly detected in Sector Gamma-7.",
    "description": "An energy signature, designated M090, has been detected exhibiting unusual fluctuations and a localized spacetime distortion. The mission requires initial reconnaissance using drone probes, followed by detailed data analysis to ascertain its properties. Avoid direct contact until further analysis is complete. Prioritize data collection on energy output, signature pattern, and gravitational effects.",
    "priority": "High",
    "assigned_agent": "AI-Sentinel-7",
    "start_date": "2023-10-27T08:00:00Z",
    "due_date": "2023-10-28T18:00:00Z",
    "phases": [
      {
        "phase_id": "P001",
        "name": "Probe Deployment & Initial Scan",
        "status": "pending",
        "tasks": [
          "Deploy three long-range probes (Designation: Pathfinder-1 to -3)",
          "Initiate wide-spectrum energy scan (Gamma, X-ray, Radio, Optical)",
          "Gather gravitational perturbation data"
        ]
      },
      {
        "phase_id": "P002",
        "name": "Data Ingestion & Preliminary Analysis",
        "status": "pending",
        "tasks": [
          "Ingest all probe telemetry",
          "Cross-reference energy signatures with known celestial and artificial phenomena databases",
          "Generate initial threat assessment report"
        ]
      },
      {
        "phase_id": "P003",
        "name": "Report Generation & Recommendations",
        "status": "pending",
        "tasks": [
          "Compile comprehensive mission report (M090-RPT-001)",
          "Formulate recommendations for next steps (e.g., closer inspection, containment, neutralization)"
        ]
      }
    ],
    "resources_allocated": [
      "3x Pathfinder-class Reconnaissance Probes",
      "Sector Gamma-7 Navigational Charts",
      "AI Core Processing Unit (Designation: 'Orion')",
      "Secure Data Uplink (Frequency: Delta-339)"
    ],
    "constraints": [
      "Minimize energy expenditure during reconnaissance",
      "Maintain a safe distance of at least 10,000 km from the anomaly's center",
      "All data to be encrypted with Level 5 protocols"
    ],
    "expected_output": {
      "type": "JSON_REPORT",
      "schema": {
        "report_id": "string",
        "mission_id": "string",
        "anomaly_signature": "object",
        "threat_assessment": "string",
        "recommendations": "array_of_strings",
        "raw_data_link": "string"
      }
    }
  },

}
